skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fellowship greenville
des: Listen to the latest message and sermons from Fellowship Greenville. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening to past messages, you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current message. You can also ask for previous and next messages by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next".
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
